title: Stenciled serif
content:
I'm trying to identify this stenciled serif typeface. It was used in a recent version of [Enroute](http://web.archive.org/web/20140828192749/http:/enroute.aircanada.com/) magazine. They don't usually create customize typefaces so I'd guess this is probably a font.
